  "pokedexDescription": "A legend tells the tale of two sisters. They sang and danced a joyous song. Until one day, the younger sister discovered a strange cacoon. The elder sister warned her not to go near, but the younger sister did not listen... The beast within the cacoon was awakened and laid waste to the valley. The elder sister tried to stop it, but to no avail. The beast took the elder sisters eyes, and in the end, nothing was left but ash and decay. Legends say that the younger sister never forgave herself. She dawned a mask as a reminder of the tragedy she caused, and hid herself from the world.",
